Package bayseanNetwork

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Score
    The Interface Score Provides a method to compute DAG scores.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DAG
    The Class DAG Provides the proper methods to create a Directed Acyclic Graph regarding some restrictions, namely the parent number each node can take
    DAGGHC
    The Class DAGGHC Contains a DAG and also a score value associated, very useful to construct the DBN.
    GHC
    The Class GHC Implements the algorithm 2, using TABU list and random restarts in order obtain the DBN
    LL
    The Class LL Implements Score; The log-likehood algorithm correctly implemented
    MDL
    The Class MDL.
    ParameterLearning
    The Class ParameterLearning.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IlegalOperation
    The Class IlegalOperation Implements exception for most commonly used DAG methods, mainely add() remove() and reverse()
    NoParent
    The Class NoParent Implements exception for DAG methods namely calcNijk, maxq, fromParentConfiguration
    PCInvalid
    The Class NoParent Implements exception if ParentConfiguration is invalid.
